response.overview: Nearly a decade after occupation by an extraterrestrial force, the lives of a Chicago neighborhood on both sides of the conflict are explored. In a working-class Chicago neighborhood occupied by an alien force for nine years, increased surveillance and the restriction of civil rights have given rise to an authoritarian system -- and dissent among the populace.
response.tagline: 10 years ago, they took our planet. Today, we take it back!
response.title: Captive State

release_dates.note: Originally rated 12A for a cancelled theatrical release
